{"tid":393461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【入黎儲口德】無綫資深演員廖麗麗舌癌病逝 享年70歲","createTime":"2017-09-09T09:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T13:26:29.000Z","uid":78546,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75edbcfa430d13a25c215f9481a039e0b0c71e50","tid":393461,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170909&amp;guid=57188240&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170909%26guid%3D57188240%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=B0JB2woox3lLUaq5Avl%2BIb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ab7776a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170909%26guid%3D57188240%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=afc71bf3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170909&amp;guid=57188240&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日《蘋果》收到消息，無綫資深演員廖麗麗日前因病逝，享年70歲。其女兒Sindy今日接受《蘋果》電話訪問，證實廖麗麗離世消息，透露其母數月前發現患上舌癌，隨後擴散到淋巴及肺部，延至本月4日凌晨不治。<br />\n<br />\n廖麗麗於2011年確診患上乳腺癌，經治療後已經康復。歐瑞偉今日接受傳媒電話訪問時說：「噚日接到消息，大家都好愕然，但唔知佢乜嘢病。」薛家燕曾與廖麗麗拍過《皆大歡喜》等劇，對於廖麗麗突然離世，家燕姐都好愕然，她說﹕「我早幾月拍《燦爛的外母》時喺化妝間撞過佢拍第二套劇，我仲問佢有冇跳拉丁舞添，佢話『有』。見佢好精神冇乜嘢喎。佢係拉丁舞高手，所以keep到個身型咁弗，聽到呢個消息真係好愕然，大家真係要珍惜身邊人。」<br />\n<br />\n廖麗麗在中日抗戰期間出世，曾經歷文化大革命，並跟隨紅衛兵到處表演兼參與批鬥。廖麗麗有過兩段婚姻及育有一女，曾為新加坡廣播電視台藝員，87年回流返港在無綫電視工作，善演帶點鄉音的三姑六婆和闊太，其中在《大時代》飾演法官、當庭訓斥丁蟹(鄭少秋飾)更令人津津樂道。'<br />\n<br />\n廖麗麗至今演出劇集逾百套，在最近一部《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》中扮演清潔阿姐。此外，廖麗麗本身亦是社交舞能手，曾在《皆大歡喜》、《天天．天晴》及其他劇集中有跳舞的演出。"},{"pid":"9b26b60e29809b6d93b9c4e1d2c805aec18f9ebb","tid":393461,"uid":92736,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"關我乜事"},{"pid":"6bdf93be795b8fb2c23cbe4a7094fb143e25f867","tid":393461,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"3956700eba14ad56cc9e9c0e59f6a6b4afe145a5","tid":393461,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"未用google check之前個腦入面係李麗麗個樣"},{"pid":"8e7a0c1eb16221f8bd0ef19ec2f868dce49c9335","tid":393461,"uid":35815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5ab7ba36c931566b21038d22835444350e3b6d2","tid":393461,"uid":4917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"原來係紅衛兵"},{"pid":"ba0f3e669de01ce5400902fb075bea2ef0fcc238","tid":393461,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"580e89242e1fec61b7ecc78ea31fe9878bb9485d","tid":393461,"uid":40682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"Fb同呢度都成班人唔睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5a0672c7b4c262c2085d5794536979e4214b06","tid":393461,"uid":53164,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"廖麗麗在中日抗戰期間出世，曾經歷文化大革命，並跟隨紅衛兵到處表演兼參與批鬥。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ef6cbda5606ecd671fd3ff9a1962da45f26014","tid":393461,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"R.I.P."},{"pid":"66b3b798d1bd9d735031d5edb657cb805d2abeb7","tid":393461,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"而廖麗麗命途很坎坷，18、9歲時在一間寄宿舞蹈學校讀書，一邊幫父親的兵工廠打工，兼且要照顧其他姊妹。學有所成之際，廖麗麗便上山下鄉，到處在農民、漁民、礦工和軍隊面前表演民族舞。不久，認識第一任丈夫結婚生兒，但因應當時的共產黨政策，規定舞蹈團成員要在適當時候才能輪流生兒育女，加上一些領導不容許她生下第一胎，廖麗麗最終被迫墮"},{"pid":"78342a2b5f2998bbdad2bb0949ab2ed3bcd932ae","tid":393461,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廖麗麗在中日抗戰期間出世，曾經歷文化大革命，並跟隨紅衛兵到處表演兼參與批鬥。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3e9179ddfe3c4e4df1574d83f9970637193c58","tid":393461,"uid":141804,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6830965ab2fdc5669307389cdcc81ecec8afef3d","tid":393461,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而廖麗麗命途很坎坷，18、9歲時在一間寄宿舞蹈學校讀書，一邊幫父親的兵工廠打工，兼且要照顧其他姊妹。學有所成之際，廖麗麗便上山下鄉，到處在農民、漁民、礦工和軍隊面前表演民族舞。不久，認識第一任丈夫結婚生兒，但因應當時的共產黨政策，規定舞蹈團成員要在適當時候才能輪流生兒育女，加上一些領導不容許她生下第一胎，廖麗麗最終被迫墮</blockquote><br />\n嘩嘩嘩<br />\n俾共匪逼過落仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75df8be818dd20c781494149e1e39b36e9799b0c","tid":393461,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:01:18.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe20e2744905683aa17c52f25e0aa2e5fb315bd","tid":393461,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"做埋紅衛兵都冇好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ccf8de0284ded35357fc204c237a8b7f66fc36","tid":393461,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"係呢度講一次RIP<br />\n可以同蔡副局講番10次恭喜"},{"pid":"99640cba5287d4a82b0fd8fb1c608b20d72a3ecf","tid":393461,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:03:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廖麗麗在中日抗戰期間出世，曾經歷文化大革命，並跟隨紅衛兵到處表演兼參與批鬥。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c3e68325ca48acf721e0e6886a928f32f09b63a2","tid":393461,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb55ab084386426efadbde9098c267b8f6c917ab","tid":393461,"uid":50374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cdbefbe724c26de06396e6adca27fedaf29101","tid":393461,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"點解脷都會有癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15391e41679a9ceae4d61b4806eb02e9eadda901","tid":393461,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解脷都會有癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇到另一段新聞咁講<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n想起亡母，Sindy悲慟哭道：「佢係一個好堅強嘅人，今年7月17號做手術，做完手術之後身體好弱。佢早幾個月發現條脷有粒細痱滋，一路都冇好，我哋都冇為意係嗰件事，冇諗到咁嚴重。」<br />\n<br />\n「後來知道係脷癌，要即刻切除癌細胞，條脷割咗一大半，講唔到嘢，食嘢都有困難，媽咪仲同我講，第時講唔到對白添，我仲同佢講健康最緊要，你乜都唔好諗。」此時Sindy再痛哭：「媽咪好勇敢，割咗大半條脷之後重新適應講嘢，但傷口係咁流血水，跟住擴散到淋巴同個肺。」</blockquote><br />\n我都係成日咬損舌頭生痱滋o既人<br />\n我都驚緊<br />\n真係唔清楚經常照鏡目測舌頭有冇得早日發現"},{"pid":"a9c97072ae81ec34916f8bc8c62312f421e208d4","tid":393461,"uid":15977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"口德分-50000會生癌<br />\n<br />\n我離死未遠已"},{"pid":"3452b1bc79170552aad0e016bea0172095222f60","tid":393461,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110ece5e2860c223b9cd784a6e877e4427d3dd28","tid":393461,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"RIP"}]}